Invocation Name: training camp
des:
Set the date for your upcoming BJJ, MMA, or any other fight competition and let Alexa remind you remaining number of days while you undergo your training camp.
After your competition date expires, you can set a new date for your future competition.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
